<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss version="2.0"><channel><title>关凯迪</title><description>关凯迪的个人站：记录 AI 内容系统、个人 IP 写作、内容流程搭建和语音输入工具探索。</description><link>https://guankaidi.com/</link><item><title>我为什么开始做个人 IP 内容</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-why-personal-ip/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-why-personal-ip/</guid><description>不是为了把自己包装得很厉害，而是因为有能力还不够，客户需要持续看见你。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>个人 IP</category><category>内容系统</category><category>交付</category></item><item><title>企业老板都在愁“AI怎么落地”，而市面上很少有人认真做这件事</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-ai-landing-translator/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-ai-landing-translator/</guid><description>中小企业并不缺 AI 焦虑，也不缺尝试意愿，真正缺的是有人能把老板的模糊需求翻译成 AI 可以执行的业务方案。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>AI落地</category><category>企业服务</category><category>AI咨询</category></item><item><title>内容系统不是资料夹</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-content-system-not-folder/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-content-system-not-folder/</guid><description>真正能帮你持续输出的，不是存了多少资料，而是资料能不能被转成选题、观点和文章。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>内容系统</category><category>AI 写作</category><category>素材整理</category></item><item><title>为什么我建议先做静态博客</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-static-blog-first/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-static-blog-first/</guid><description>如果目标是长期写内容，而不是折腾服务器，静态博客通常是更轻、更安全的起点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>建站</category><category>Cloudflare Pages</category><category>内容系统</category></item><item><title>想让 AI 写得像你，先让它看懂你的改稿</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-teach-ai-your-style/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-teach-ai-your-style/</guid><descr